title: Fighters react to 'The Korean Zombie' Chan Sung Jung's KO win in Houston
text:
Feb 5, 2017 at 2:01a ET 0Shares 
Former title challenger Chan Sung Jung reintroduced himself to the UFC in a big way Saturday night when he KOed ninth-ranked featherweight Dennis Bermudez in the first round of their main event bout at UFC Houston. 
Jung has posted finishes in his last four wins and despite his three-year layoff, quickly reclaimed his title as one of the most exciting fighters on the roster. Check out what other UFC fighters had to say about The Korean Zombieâ€™s big performance.
